mwangilink@gmail.com In an era where armed bank robberies have been replaced by cyber fraud, two of Kenya’s most notorious criminals, Githenji and Kiriamiti, know they would definitely not fit. One of Kenya’s most read novels, My Life in Crime, is being made into a blockbuster movie. Uganda, Ethiopia, Somalia and Sudan have been experiencing internal conflicts. US president-elect praises voters for casting ballots in record numbers on November 3.